# Default policy: TDB bytes don't get redistributed through git, because
# some indexed sources are paywalled or by-author-permission. Track only
# the manifest and citation sidecars by default.
*.tdb
*.TDB
*.tdb.txt
*.TDB.txt

# Always keep:
!README.md
!.gitignore
!_manifest.yaml
!*.citation.yaml

# ── Per-system corpus directories the user has explicitly chosen ──
# ── to share. These OVERRIDE the global *.tdb gitignore above. ────
# When adding a new system, mirror this pattern: list the dir name
# (so .tdb files inside are tracked) AND any subdirectories.
!Co-Cr/
!Co-Cr/**
!Co-Cr-Ni/
!Co-Cr-Ni/**
!Co-Ni/
!Co-Ni/**
!Cr-Ni/
!Cr-Ni/**
